  "synopsis": "This is a dream of a girl who is imagining to be a bird. The title \"tayutaum\" is a combination of the words: \"tayutau yume (floating dream)\", \"hakuchuumu (daydream)\", and \"aquarium\". I want the audience to feel the physical sensation of flying in the sky or floating in the water.\n\n(Source: Official Site)",
